  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if [C-11]NOP-1A receptor binding (VT) can be altered by an intravenous
      hydrocortisone (cortisol) challenge through CRF-NOP interactions
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Examines changes in [C-11]NOP-1A pharmacokinetics caused by an intravenous hydrocortisone
      challenge (1 mg/kg)
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
